- Simple word guessing game, the theme is movie genres.
- 4 total genres to guess from: horror, romance, action, comedy
- 3 total chances to guess the word; lists letters
- Single player game. 
- The game does NOT tell the player the position of letters in the word.
- A playerâ€™s final score is the number of turns (letter guesses) they made before guessing the correct
word. Lower scores are better.
